    "Disinfo_cases_en": "The readers of the French newspaper Le Figaro do not believe in the hysteria surrounding the allegedly probable Russian invasion of Ukraine's territory. They believe that it is actually Kyiv that is preparing to invade the Donbas and return to active hostilities in the region.",
    "Date": "15/12/2021",
